OL,3,CWhat is the noble false widow and are
OL,4,Cspider bites on the rise in England?
OL,6,F"The most dangerous spider in Britain"
OL,7,Fhas been blamed for the number of
OL,8,Fpeople seeking hospital treatment for
OL,9,Fspider bites doubling in a decade.
OL,11,FProvisional NHS figures have shown
OL,12,Fthere were 100 admissions due to
OL,13,F"contact with or toxic effect of
OL,14,Fspiders" in the last year, according
OL,15,Fto a freedom of information request by
OL,16,FPA.
OL,26,@uD@AOUvD@HO]
