OL,3,CWhat is the noble false widow and are
OL,4,Cspider bites on the rise in England?
OL,6,FAcademics have linked the rise to an
OL,7,Fincrease in the noble false widow
OL,8,Fspider, a species which was described
OL,9,Fas "the most dangerous spider breeding
OL,10,Fin Britain" in a 2020 paper by Oxford
OL,11,FUniversity ecologist Clive Hambler,
OL,12,Fwho believes the days of treating
OL,13,Fspiders as "benign in Britain are
OL,14,Fover".
OL,16,FWhat is a noble false widow spider,
OL,17,Fand how worried should we be about a
OL,18,Fpopulation "explosion" of the species?
OL,20,FWhat is a false widow spider?
OL,26,@qD@DOUvD@EO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/15
