OL,3,CWhat is the noble false widow and are
OL,4,Cspider bites on the rise in England?
OL,6,FDanniella Sherwood from the charity
OL,7,FBuglife says the noble false widow
OL,8,F"can be easily recognised by the white
OL,9,Fand black pattern of the abdomen,
OL,10,Fwhich is often likened to being shaped
OL,11,Flike a skull, and its robust legs and
OL,12,Flong carapace."
OL,14,FWhere will you likely find the noble
OL,15,Ffalse widow?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
