OL,3,CWhat is the noble false widow and are
OL,4,Cspider bites on the rise in England?
OL,6,FDr Michel Dugon, a zoologist
OL,7,Fspecialising in the evolution and
OL,8,Fdevelopment of venom systems at the
OL,9,FUniversity of Galway, says that the
OL,10,Fnoble false widow prefers "to live in
OL,11,Fand around houses rather than in
OL,12,Fnatural habitats, at least in the UK
OL,13,Fand Ireland".
OL,15,FThe species' webs are usually
OL,16,Fsuspended at least 1.5 metres off the
OL,17,Fground, which allows the spiders to
OL,18,Fhunt flying insects, according to the
OL,19,FNatural History Museum.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
