PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1776103865
OL,3,CWhat is the noble false widow and are
OL,4,Cspider bites on the rise in England?
OL,6,FIn homes, they often prefer to hide
OL,7,Ftucked away in conservatories or
OL,8,Fkitchens, sheds and garages.
OL,10,FAre spider bites on the rise?
OL,12,FA Freedom of Information request by PA
OL,13,Frevealed that of the 100 admissions
OL,14,Flast year, 73 of these came through
OL,15,FA&E. This compares to 38 of the 47 in
OL,16,F2015.
OL,18,FThere were 43 hospital admissions due
OL,19,Fto spider bites in 2021, and the
OL,20,Ffigure increased to 95 the following
OL,21,Fyear, the NHS figures show.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
