PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1776103865
OL,3,CWhat is the noble false widow and are
OL,4,Cspider bites on the rise in England?
OL,6,FIn both 2023 and 2024, there were 91
OL,7,Fadmissions.
OL,9,FMr Hambler, who is a lecturer in
OL,10,Fbiological and human sciences at
OL,11,FHertford College, says that people are
OL,12,Fcoming into contact with false widow
OL,13,Fspiders much more often than they
OL,14,Frealise.
OL,16,F"The incidents of severe bites from
OL,17,Fspiders in Britain have increased, as
OL,18,Fthis species (false widows) has become
OL,19,Fhugely more abundant in Britain,
OL,20,Fparticularly in the south."
OL,26,@xD@AOU|D@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/15
