PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1776103865
OL,3,CWhat is the noble false widow and are
OL,4,Cspider bites on the rise in England?
OL,6,FDr Dugon says the hospital admission
OL,7,Ffigures are "interesting" but "not
OL,8,Fsurprising", pinning the rise in bites
OL,9,Fneeding treatment on the "explosion in
OL,10,Fthe population of noble false widow".
OL,12,FBut spider bites may be increasingly
OL,13,Fmisdiagnosed due to an increased media
OL,14,Fcoverage on false widows and spider
OL,15,Fbites over the last few years.
OL,17,F"Essentially, when you do not see the
OL,18,Fspider really bite or capture the
OL,19,Fspider and you say that you haven't
OL,20,Ffelt any pain ` then it's most likely
OL,21,Fnot a spider," Dr Dugon added.
OL,26,@oD@MOUoD@YO]oD@_OUpD@KO]qD@ZOUyD@AOU}D@
