CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1776103865
OL,3,CWhat is the noble false widow and are
OL,4,Cspider bites on the rise in England?
OL,6,F"Because a bite by the noble false
OL,7,Fwidow will actually wake you up. The
OL,8,Fpain is equivalent to a wasp sting or
OL,9,Feven more than that."
OL,11,FHow will I know if it is a spider bite?
OL,13,FAccording to the charity Buglife, the
OL,14,Ffalse widow spider may leave small
OL,15,Fpuncture marks on the skin and can
OL,16,Fcause localised pain and swelling.
OL,18,FThe pain is comparable to a bee or
OL,19,Fwasp sting and is usually resolved
OL,20,Fwithin one to 12 hours after the bite.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30311
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1776103865
OL,3,CWhat is the noble false widow and are
OL,4,Cspider bites on the rise in England?
OL,6,FSome people may experience nausea or
OL,7,Fheadaches, which will typically
OL,8,Falleviate within two to three days.
OL,10,FNoble false widow spiders mostly occur
OL,11,Fas a result of the spiders being
OL,12,Fpushed against human skin, through
OL,13,Favenues such as being rolled on in
OL,14,Fbed, trapped in clothing, or squashed
OL,15,Fin shoes.
OL,17,F"This spider does not actively seek
OL,18,Fout and bite humans unprovoked,"
OL,19,FBuglife said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
