PN,30314
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1776103865
OL,3,CWhat is the noble false widow and are
OL,4,Cspider bites on the rise in England?
OL,6,FShould we be concerned about the false
OL,7,Fwidow?
OL,9,FDr Dugon said that spiders are "not
OL,10,Faggressive animals" and "don't
OL,11,Fparticularly try to bite", adding that
OL,12,F100 cases in England are relatively
OL,13,Fminor.
OL,15,FAdam Hart, a professor of science
OL,16,Fcommunication at the University of
OL,17,FGloucestershire, said that while false
OL,18,Fwidows have "expanded their range",
OL,19,Fthere is no strong reason for the
OL,20,Fpublic to be concerned about the
OL,21,Fspecies.
OL,26,@qD@`OUrD@SO]rD@YOUsD@YO]zD@MOUzD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/15
