OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30315
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1776103865
OL,3,CWhat is the noble false widow and are
OL,4,Cspider bites on the rise in England?
OL,6,FHe said: "While they can bite if
OL,7,Fhandled or trapped against the skin,
OL,8,Fmost bites are mild, and severe
OL,9,Freactions are rare.
OL,11,F"Basic precautions, such as not
OL,12,Fhandling spiders directly, should
OL,13,Fensure the chances of being bitten are
OL,14,Fminuscule."
